However, after reading all this big discussion on charm nerf, and the patch date being changed to April 1st...I don't think it's gonna happen; at least not to the level discussed.  I don't beleive SoE is trying to remove charming as a XPing solo tactic.  I think they want to prevent a very small number of players taking advantage of their bad game design.  You don't want a single player soloing minis, or even bosses.  It's not in the vision of balance for the game, I'm pretty sure.<br>
